9 shots\n|goalie3-2   =[[Cristobal Huet]] 27 saves / 32 shots\n\n|date4       =April 17\n|score4      =3\u20134\n|ot4         =2\n|won4        =1\n|recap4      =www.nhl.com/scores/htmlreports/20072008/GS030134.HTM\n|4-1-1       =00:42 \u2013 [[Jeff Carter]] (2)<br>18:33 \u2013 Jeff Carter (3)\n|4-1-2       =[[Nicklas B\u00e4ckstr\u00f6m|Nicklas Backstrom]] (1) \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 02:41<br>[[Alexander Semin]] (1) \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 12:59\n|4-2-1       =''No scoring''\n|4-2-2       =[[Steve Eminger]] (1) \u2013 05:56\n|4-3-1       =10:01 \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 [[Daniel Bri\u00e8re|Daniel Briere]] (5)\n|4-3-2       =''No scoring''\n|4-4-1       =06:40 \u2013 [[Mike Knuble]] (2)\n|4-4-2       =''No scoring''\n|goalie4-1   =[[Martin Biron]] 38 saves / 41 shots\n|goalie4-2   =[[Cristobal Huet]] 42 saves / 46 shots\n\n|date5       =April 19\n|score5      =2\u20133\n|won5        =2\n|recap5      =www.nhl.com/scores/htmlreports/20072008/GS030135.HTM\n|5-1-1       =''No scoring''\n|5-1-2       =07:31 \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 [[Nicklas B\u00e4ckstr\u00f6m|Nicklas Backstrom]] (2)\n|5-2-1       =[[V\u00e1clav Prospal|Vaclav Prospal]] (3) \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 12:35\n|5-2-2       =01:25 \u2013 [[Sergei Fedorov]] (1)\n|5-3-1       =[[Derian Hatcher]] (1) \u2013 15:17\n|5-3-2       =14:33 \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 [[Alexander Semin]] (2)\n|goalie5-1   =[[Martin Biron]] 23 saves / 26 shots\n|goalie5-2   =[[Cristobal Huet]] 30 saves / 32 shots\n\n|date6       =April 21\n|score6      =4\u20132\n|won6        =2\n|recap6      =www.nhl.com/scores/htmlreports/20072008/GS030136.HTM\n|6-1-1       =03:49 \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 [[Mike Richards]] (2)\n|6-1-2       =''No scoring''\n|6-2-1       =01:18 \u2013 ''pp'' \u2013 [[Daniel Bri\u00e8re|Daniel Briere]] (6)\n|6-2-2       =[[Nicklas B\u00e4ckstr\u00f6m|Nicklas Backstrom]] (3) \u2013 09:34<br>[[Alexander Semin]] (3) \u2013 18:03\n|6-3-1       =''No scoring''\n|6-3-2       =[[Alexander Ovechkin]] (2) \u2013 02:46<br>Alexander Ovechkin (3) \u2013 ''pp'' 